    "sections": {
        "description": "<p>Simply the easiest way to add a topbar to your website. This plugin adds a simple and clean notification bar at the top of your website, allowing you to display a nice message to your visitors as well as a custom link. What you see is what you get, and it\u2019s totally free.<\/p>\n<h4>No limitation for the Free version<\/h4>\n<p>The Free version of the Top Bar plugin is <strong>not limited<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<p>The <a href=\"https:\/\/wpdarko.com\/items\/top-bar-pro\/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">PRO version<\/a> gives you access to a lot of new features: allow users to <strong>close the Top Bar<\/strong>, choose an <strong>initial state<\/strong>, add a <strong>bottom border<\/strong>, set a <strong>time before the Top Bar appears<\/strong>, bottom positioning, user visibility settings (<strong>only for guests or registered users<\/strong>), change the <strong>font-size<\/strong>&#8230;<\/p>\n<h4>Fully translatable<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>POT files included (\/lang\/)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>Available fields\/options<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Status (active or inactive)<\/li>\n<li>Stay visible when scrolling<\/li>\n<li>Message (obviously)<\/li>\n<li>Button text<\/li>\n<li>Button URL<\/li>\n<li>Color<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>Usage<\/h4>\n<p>Go to <a href=\"https:\/\/wpdarko.com\/support\/docs\/get-started-with-the-top-bar-plugin\/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">the plugin&#8217;s documentation<\/a> if you need more information on how to use this plugin.<\/p>\n<h4>Support<\/h4>\n<p>Find help on <a href=\"https:\/\/wpdarko.com\/support\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">our support platform<\/a> for this plugin (we\u2019ll answer you fast, promise).<\/p>\n",
        "installation": "<h4>Installation<\/h4>\n<ol>\n<li>In your WordPress admin panel, go to Plugins &gt; New Plugin<\/li>\n<li>Find our Top Bar plugin by WP Darko and click Install now<\/li>\n<li>Alternatively, download the plugin and upload the contents of top-bar.zip to your plugins directory, which usually is \/wp-content\/plugins\/<\/li>\n<li>Activate the plugin<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<h4>Usage<\/h4>\n<p>Go to <a href=\"https:\/\/wpdarko.com\/support\/docs\/get-started-with-the-top-bar-plugin\/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">the plugin&#8217;s documentation<\/a> for information on how to use it.<\/p>\n",
        "faq": "\n<dt id='no%20limitation%20for%20the%20free%20version'>\nNo limitation for the Free version\n<\/h4>\n<p>\n<p>The Free version of the Top Bar plugin is <strong>not limited<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<p>The <a href=\"https:\/\/wpdarko.com\/items\/top-bar-pro\/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">PRO version<\/a> gives you access to a lot of new features: allow users to <strong>close the Top Bar<\/strong>, choose an <strong>initial state<\/strong>, add a <strong>bottom border<\/strong>, set a <strong>time before the Top Bar appears<\/strong>, bottom positioning, user visibility settings (<strong>only for guests or registered users<\/strong>), change the <strong>font-size<\/strong>&#8230;<\/p>\n<\/p>\n<dt id='fully%20translatable'>\nFully translatable\n<\/h4>\n<p>\n<ul>\n<li>POT files included (\/lang\/)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/p>\n<dt id='usage'>\nUsage\n<\/h4>\n<p>\n<p>Go to <a href=\"https:\/\/wpdarko.com\/support\/docs\/get-started-with-the-top-bar-plugin\/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">the plugin&#8217;s documentation<\/a> if you need more information on how to use this plugin.<\/p>\n<\/p>\n<dt id='support'>\nSupport\n<\/h4>\n<p>\n<p>Find help on <a href=\"https:\/\/wpdarko.com\/support\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">our support platform<\/a> for this plugin (we\u2019ll answer you fast, promise).<\/p>\n<\/p>\n\n",
        "changelog": "<h4>3.0.6<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed minor vulnerability issue<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>3.0.5<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed minor vulnerability issue<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>3.0.4<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Security update<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>3.0.3<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Replaced deprecated jQuery methods<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>3.0.2<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixes JS bug with settings<\/li>\n<li>Fixes issues with specific character in the message<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>3.0<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixes CSS issues<\/li>\n<li>Fixes JS issues<\/li>\n<li>[New feature] Detect fixed navigation (automatically finds and fixes conflicts)<\/li>\n<li>[New feature] Button link behavior (same\/new window)<\/li>\n<li>Updated setting panel<\/li>\n<li>Updated admin menus<\/li>\n<li>Better fonts for message\/button<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>2.0<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Adds cleaner and faster option screen<\/li>\n<li>Fixes CSS issues<\/li>\n<li>Fixes JS issues<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.2<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Plugin is now translation ready<\/li>\n<li>Added French translation<\/li>\n<li>Added Spanish translation<\/li>\n<li>Minor CSS fixes<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.1<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Cleaning code<\/li>\n<li>Minor bug fixes<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.0<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Initial release<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n",
        "screenshots": "<ol><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/top-bar\/assets\/screenshot-1.png?rev=1036415\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/top-bar\/assets\/screenshot-1.png?rev=1036415\" alt=\"Top Bar (front view)\"><\/a><p>Top Bar (front view)<\/p><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/top-bar\/assets\/screenshot-2.png?rev=1950295\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/top-bar\/assets\/screenshot-2.png?rev=1950295\" alt=\"Configuring the Top Bar (admin view)\"><\/a><p>Configuring the Top Bar (admin view)<\/p><\/li><\/ol>",
        "reviews": "<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Does exactly what it describes<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/iworks\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/c2ad634813e4462f0532a9cf0c903e2c?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/c2ad634813e4462f0532a9cf0c903e2c?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/iworks\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Marcin Pietrzak <small>(iworks)<\/small><\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">March 25, 2024<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">Does exactly what it describes. Nothing less, nothing more. I like it!<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Very, very limited<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"2 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"2\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/estudiobla\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/5ea0f0d82421ac2b7a1a8e92fe343170?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/5ea0f0d82421ac2b7a1a8e92fe343170?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/estudiobla\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">estudiobla<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">December 5, 2023<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">You can't change the color of the text, it's always white. And apparently you can't change it with code either.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Doesn&#039;t work well \/ difficult uninstallation<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"3 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"3\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/jakours2\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/b0ea5958633d819a106892a8e1c9e9b2?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/b0ea5958633d819a106892a8e1c9e9b2?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/jakours2\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Jakours2<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">January 15, 2023<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Doesn't work well with Salient theme. When uninstalling, the plugin would not uninstall cleanly. It was giving a critical error message. I uninstalled it through cPanel. I have used it several times in the past with no problems. Maybe it needs an update?<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Horrible customer service and business practices<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/billfox2022\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/c0b3d506caa344692488fdfc426a2371?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/c0b3d506caa344692488fdfc426a2371?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/billfox2022\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">billfox2022<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">July 27, 2022<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">Top Bar works well enough but engages in abusive business practices. They do not send a notification before they automatically renew your license. In my case, I no longer needed an unlimited license and asked support to please change my license to a single site and refund the difference via a support ticket. They didn't email a copy of the submission and never responded in any way to my request. After a week or two, I sent a direct email to their support. Still waiting after one month for any response. I have canceled my subscription and won't do business with this company again. I replaced Topbar with Notibar. A fantastic replacement that has more flexible appearance options and it's free!<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Excellent<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/forsteps\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/1189f2a4dad68d22175541ff8d2c13dc?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/1189f2a4dad68d22175541ff8d2c13dc?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/forsteps\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">forsteps<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">April 4, 2022<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">Simple and excellent! Does what it says.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Doesn&#039;t work<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/dvapps\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/d3ab0813ee26b47d3891425b8e4a9e9a?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/d3ab0813ee26b47d3891425b8e4a9e9a?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/dvapps\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Divanshu <small>(dvapps)<\/small><\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">March 3, 2022<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">None of the options save<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t